item.dc:creator: @junkj junkj
item.description:
@junkj wrote:

SendKeys?

If you have SRL—Scar recource library-- or however you spell it
Put
{.include srl/srl.scar}
Under program;

Then instead of Sendkeys use Typsend

Then under that click mouse Put a few spaces

Then put

Begin
SetUpSRL;
ActivateClient;
ClearDebug;
(The writelns here)
end.

O wait i almost forgot

Put
TerminateScript;

Under that last clickmouse

Then thats all!

Glad i can help!
